{"tid":1236682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新戰線】大家一齊制裁CCTVB","createTime":"2019-06-17T13:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T22:41:15.000Z","uid":15276,"like":109,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"310dd390d61003fb4eab465e51a77e51dbb7b4de","tid":1236682,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N4OOfXu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4OOfXu.png&h=9345540b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家CCTVB資訊封鎖、歪曲事實嘅程度已經同CCTV無分別<br />\n大家理應當佢地同黑警一樣待遇<br />\n<br />\n第一步：Cut台、叫屋企人唔好睇<br />\n<br />\n第二步：不招待不服務TVB員工、不接受TVB訪問、見到佢地採訪就屌走佢地<br />\n<br />\n第三步：將CCTVB新聞部嘅人起底，就算底層只係聽指示，但佢地都係同流合污出賣緊香港人，有良知就唔該唔好再做CCTVB<br />\n<br />\n好重要，希望大家盡力做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef435fe8711948a023b35675924ca6d9c313a19","tid":1236682,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65aea66746936ba9f7f90b0d0ea0588cba6302df","tid":1236682,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c2dc9df60ed9b49eaad04f998796f3ed634ab7","tid":1236682,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"方向正確，佢地已經收哂Ｄ牌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今後議題 - 文宣組常態化 &amp; 71要求政改 &amp; 2020年9月立法會選戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232620/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232620/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n希望成立「文宣台」以助對抗長輩圖及增加國際影響力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1236602/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1236602/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"da44d4f9b21b4c80590f82386db3445062e233e3","tid":1236682,"uid":29675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"