emove-j5-guide%2Ftop-news%2Famp%2F&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=f3fb1742\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2016/02/23/hkppl-remove-j5-guide/top-news/amp/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊del佢老母台！<br />\n遲不疑遲！！<br />\ndel佢老母！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"嬲到打錯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事不疑遲！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"01162d3f61c174ffa98d739a4dcdb855f6900d8e","tid":1236682,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://corporate.tvb.com/article/17.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.tvb.com%2Farticle%2F17.html&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=d51933e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://corporate.tvb.com/article/17.html</a><br />\n無線管理層列表<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人搵到現職主播名單？<br />\n同埋linkedin搵tvb新聞部既人諗唔諗得過？"},{"pid":"321ba9f53b42bc049fa73135b9bc842ec57393b4","tid":1236682,"uid":252296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:32:55.000Z","msg":"TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=bcb49c06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導"},{"pid":"d016b46998a3842dd6771b08b75a53596f820f11","tid":1236682,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01162d3f61c174ffa98d739a4dcdb855f6900d8e","tid":1236682,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://corporate.tvb.com/article/17.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.tvb.com%2Farticle%2F17.html&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=d51933e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://corporate.tvb.com/article/17.html</a><br />\n無線管理層列表<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人搵到現職主播名單？<br />\n同埋linkedin搵tvb新聞部既人諗唔諗得過？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216951/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216951/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"150bfb298b9f834e11a25f0618a1307516bc30db","tid":1236682,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b2983cbab8fd6de9abc3f0e6f5aabfabb3bb6c","tid":1236682,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d016b46998a3842dd6771b08b75a53596f820f11","tid":1236682,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01162d3f61c174ffa98d739a4dcdb855f6900d8e","tid":1236682,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://corporate.tvb.com/article/17.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.tvb.com%2Farticle%2F17.html&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=d51933e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://corporate.tvb.com/article/17.html</a><br />\n無線管理層列表<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人搵到現職主播名單？<br />\n同埋linkedin搵tvb新聞部既人諗唔諗得過？"},"c